skins.shipDescription: Tennessee-class battleship ¨C California, Hull Number BB-44!
skins.selfIntroduction: Hello. I am the second of the Tennessee class battleships, California. I was once the flagship of the Pacific fleet, and was part of the Atlantic fleet as well. How about it? Bet you didn't expect that I was a popular one, did you? Hehe~
skins.acquisition: Hello, Commander. I am California. It's not good to brag, but I'm quite strong you know. Do look forward to it~
skins.login: Weather, check. Wind, check. A fine sailing day, Commander.
skins.details: Commander, I will do my best to meet everyone's expectations
skins.secretaryIdle1: I feel different from big sister? That's not true. She might not look it but she's actually kind
skins.secretaryIdle2: Ah~ Big sis didn't say much today... Wha! N-nothing at all!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Ah, where did my undies go? Eheh
skins.secretaryTouch: This is comfy. Every time big sis scolds me, she comforts me with this afterwards as well.
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Wait-... Commander! Where are you touching? Big sis wouldn't do this!
